  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nThis is not the `dialProtocol` timeout issue in #1597 since we got the stream (I applied my hot fix #1600 for my local branch). After that we receive no response from the peer and regular sync stalled.\r\n\r\n```\r\n2020-10-15 14:13:49 [SYNC]             info: Regular Sync: Requesting blocks from slot 501677 to slot 501740\r\n2020-10-15 14:13:49 [SYNC]             info: Regular Sync: Synced up to slot 501676  currentSlot=516668, gossipParentBlockRoot=undefined\r\n2020-10-15 14:13:50 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: sending beacon_blocks_by_range request to 16Uiu2HAmBHHixkAU7ikai94zvxWgbJS4J9BBNr2ZsHkAt4ghWCBd requestId=f69141a4794db63f, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n2020-10-15 14:13:59 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: got stream to 16Uiu2HAmBHHixkAU7ikai94zvxWgbJS4J9BBNr2ZsHkAt4ghWCBd requestId=f69141a4794db63f, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nWe should either receive/trigger an error or the log `receive beacon_blocks_by_range request from` with same requestId.\r\n\r\nI still saw the peer stay connected to us after that:\r\n```\r\n2020-10-15 14:14:17 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: receive ping request from 16Uiu2HAmBHHixkAU7ikai94zvxWgbJS4J9BBNr2ZsHkAt4ghWCBd requestId=d7c30682f8f20c01, encoding=ssz_snapp\r\n```\r\nand after that we did do beacon_blocks_by_root request to the same peer successfully too:\r\n```\r\n2020-10-15 14:14:24 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: sending beacon_blocks_by_root request to 16Uiu2HAmBHHixkAU7ikai94zvxWgbJS4J9BBNr2ZsHkAt4ghWCBd requestId=8a24e9262bff231f, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n2020-10-15 14:14:25 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: got stream to 16Uiu2HAmBHHixkAU7ikai94zvxWgbJS4J9BBNr2ZsHkAt4ghWCBd requestId=8a24e9262bff231f, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n2020-10-15 14:14:26 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: receive beacon_blocks_by_root response with 1 chunks from 16Uiu2HAmBHHixkAU7ikai94zvxWgbJS4J9BBNr2ZsHkAt4ghWCBd requestId=8a24e9262bff231f, encoding=ssz_snappy, body=[\"0xe653c0f2da2a8edd3d8cc6e9301896d306246064d3baa3503388433c6421b8e2\"]\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis is the 1st time I see the issue, it's so rare.\r\n",
